creator: Quaint Game Studio
descriptionHtml:
This is a new endless car traffic racing game, tight your seat belt, and enjoy the high-speed racing. 🏎️

Extreme Turbo Car Racing: Traffic Simulator is the most thrilling, super charged pace simulator for car racing lovers to burn rubber and race for king of speed on android devices! 🔧

This car racing is the ultimate race on lane streets traffic, featuring numerous worlds class sports cars, tons of customizations, stunning optimized graphics, immersing gameplay, intense Nitro booster, and realistic traffic condition! 🚗

There are various environmental conditions and themes sunny, rainy, and night modes. 🌨️

This game contains single-way, two-way, time mode, and fun bomb monster truck modes. 🚎

How to Play: 🎮

- Tilt or Touch buttons to steer the car.
- Touch the gas button to accelerate.
- Use Nitro to boost your speed.
- Touch the brake button to slow down.
- Avoid colliding with other vehicles to make a high score and earn more coins.
- Upgrade your current sports car or buy a new high-performance car.
- Customise and stylize your car.

Features: ✨

- Realistic car physics, suspensions, brake effects, steering.
- Stunning 3D graphics
- Smooth and realistic car handling
- Awesome Expensive cars to choose from
- 3 detailed environments: highway, rainy, and city night
- Rich types of NPC traffic including trucks, buses and cars.
- Exclusive Customization of tires, car colors, tools, and more
- Avoid Traffic Vehicles Buses, Trucks and Cars
- Awesome music.
-Thrilling car sound and SFX.

Environment:
